                <div class="content_box">
                    <strong class="v_tit"><a href="/Cases/CasesDownLoad/1/7629" target="_blank">查看全文</a>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<a href="/Cases/Search">案例查询</a></strong>

                    <table cellspacing="2" cellpadding="0" style="margin:auto; width:750px;" class="infotable">

                        <tbody>
                            <tr><td colspan="2" height="30px" style="font-weight:bold; font-size:14px; background-color:#CCCCCC; padding-left:10px;">显示案例信息</td></tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例编号：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">FAM-1276</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">被浏览次数：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">3273 次</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">A公司“内外兼修”的采购方案何以破解订单农业履约难题？</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译名：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">How does Company A’s “internal and external” procurement plan solve the problem of contract farming performance?</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例作者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">张雪娇，邓德强，尹露群，黄炜</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">作者单位：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">南京林业大学</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">指导者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例企业名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">福州万顺和贸易有限公司</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">行业：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">农林牧副渔业</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">规模：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及的职能领域：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">采购供应部门</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例语种：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例正文页数（页）：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">9 页</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例类型：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">决策型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">订单农业；采购与付款内部控制；内部控制缺陷；2023百优案例；微案例</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">Contract farming; Internal control of purchase and payment; Internal control weaknesses</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文摘要：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">订单农业作为一种“先定向销售、后定向种植”的新型农业生产经营模式，具备“有效抵御销售风险、合理保护农户收益”的优势，对稳定农产品供销关系，实现农业产业化发展具有重要意义。农户作为定向种植环节的主力军，其能否履约践诺、按时交付合规农产品是订单农业后端销售能否成行、农业产业化能否落地见效的关键所在。本案例复现了A公司遭遇的三次大量农户违约事件，从内部控制视角分析了订单农业采购业务频繁遭遇农户违约的主要原因，解析了A公司为破解订单农业履约难题而打造的“内外兼修”的采购方案，进而还原了A公司订单农业农户违约率最终实现“由高到低”的发展历程。本案例旨在引导学员思考企业如何破解订单农业履约难题，从而实现订单农业惠农利企双赢目标。</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文摘要： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;word-break:keep-all">Contract farming is a new form of agricultural production and management model of “first directed sales, then directed planting”, which is important to stabilize the supply and marketing relationship of agricultural products and realize agricultural industrialization. As the main force in directional planting, whether the farmers can fulfill their promises and deliver compliant agricultural products timely is the key to the success of the back-end sales of contract farming and the effectiveness of agricultural industrialization. This case restates the three farmers’ defaults encountered by Company A, analyzes the main reasons for frequent farmers’ defaults in the contract farming procurement business from the perspective of internal control, and summarizes the “internal and external” procurement solution created by Company A. This case aims to guide participants to consider how to solve the contract farming defaults to achieve the win-win goal of farmers and enterprises.</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用对象： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">硕士生,工商管理硕士（MBA）,</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">编写方式：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">采编/一手资料编写</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例年代：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2022</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用课程：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">《内部控制》</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及理论知识：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">采购与付款内部控制；内部控制缺陷及其整改措施；风险控制的基本方法</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例入库时间：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2023-10</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
